Q?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>此外，预定从 7 月 1 日星期六 21:00 开始进行现场直播。</p><p>点击此处查看 Hololive Summer 2022 总导演兼制片人的采访文章。 <br /><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="card shadow overflow-hidden"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2022/09/202209091644290000.jpg"></div><div class="card-body mg-card-text p-2 p-lg-3"><h3 class="h6 mt-0 mw-0 mb-1 p-0 card-title mg-card-title mg-text-break-all text-dark font-weight-normal"> 《Holo Live Summer 2022》为何复活？导演与制片人畅谈大型项目全貌</h3><div class="text-gray mg-mogura-card-excerpt mb-1 my-md-2">2019年举办并广受好评的“Holo Live Summer 2022”今年将时隔三年再次复活。以Hololive所属VTuber专用泳衣、浴衣等特别服装的公开为首，还将发布原创歌曲、销售夏季漫画商品等。</div> <span class="badge badge-outline-live mg-mogura-card-badge px-2">Hololive</span> <span class="text-muted small ml-1">2022.09.09</span></div></div></div></div></p><p> （参考） <a href="https://twitter.com/hololivetv/status/1674387249331585025" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方推特</a></p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/hololive-summer-2023/">举办“Holo Live Summer 2023”帖子！前往长夏岛的PV已经公开，这次印尼英语也参与了</a>在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>的首发。</p> ;
